sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User/Caller
  participant QA as Answerer
  participant IR as SectionRetriever
  participant CR as ChunkRetriever
  participant LLM as Local LLM
  U->>QA: question
  QA->>IR: retrieve sections(query)
  IR-->>QA: top sections
  QA->>CR: retrieve chunks(query, section_ids)
  CR-->>QA: top micro-chunks w/ timestamps
  QA->>LLM: prompt(context=sections+chunks)
  LLM-->>QA: draft answer
  QA-->>U: answer + citations
